@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jplbpw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((0.92 / (tmp + 0.34 * v2 + 0.77)) - v2)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin((v2 + 0.46 - v1 + 0.19)))
    v2 = (0.40 - tmp)
    v2 = (v0 + 0.37)
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.76) + ((v1 + 0.13 - v2 + 0.86) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.18)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.04)) * 0.22)
    data[tid] = v0
